dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: This data set contains County Parks, Parks Dept. properties, and the two major trail properties. Other derivative data sets contain trails only and Parks property.            Park boundaries are registered with the Integrated Land Record (ILR) data set. Parks data is updated as new information becomes available.The coverage and shapefile are derived from a master data set containing additional features. Derivative data sets are refreshed when the master data set is updated.
dc_publisher_s: Snohomish County (WA) Geographic Information System (Snohomish GIS)
